#: ../../source/example.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Parameter adjustment techniques, the following techniques are also "
"applicable to other physics engines**"
msgstr ""
"**パラメータ調整テクニック、以下のテクニックは他の物理エンジンにも適用で"
